high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Slice the tomato in the refrigerator.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the refrigerator.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the stove.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter in front of the sink.
Put the cooked tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the opposite end of the counter, so you're facing the space left of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle.
Carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and slice the tomato on the second shelf next to the white mug.
Turn back around and carry the knife to the sink.
Place the knife in the kitchen sink.
Turn and cross the room to stand in front of the fridge again.
Open the fridge and take out a slice of tomato you just cut.
Carry the slice of tomato to stand in front of the stove.
Place the tomato in the microwave above the stove, turn it on, and then remove once heated.
Turn and carry the slice of tomato to the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Move to face the the knife on the counter left of the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
Move right then right again to the fridge
Open the fridge to slice the tomato inside, close the fridge
Carry the knife over to the kitchen sink
Place the knife in the kitchen sink on the right side blade down
Move back to the fridge
Open the fridge and remove a tomato slice in the fridge then shut the fridge
Carry the tomato slice over to the microwave above the stove top
Place the tomato slice inside of the microwave above the stove, heat it then remove it
Move back to the sink where the knife is
Place the tomato in the sink, left of the knife
anns.task_desc: Slice a warn tomato to place in the sink
